item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Elton John Discography in either 24bit or 16bit FLAC
item.description:
Greetings,

Sir Elton John recently announced that he ended his 52 years of touring career. It will be fantastic that the community honor him by listening to his songs, thus please share Elton John's complete discography in either 24bit or 16bit FLAC.

Many thanks in advance.
item.author: AudioKingpin
